4/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598629" class="wp-caption-text">费耶·韦伯斯特。图片来源：迈克尔·蒂龙·德莱尼</figcaption></figure><p>“Noise For Now”旨在让艺术家与美国各地从事生殖正义工作的草根组织建立联系，努力为他们提供经济支持和更广泛的认识。</p><p><strong>现在的噪音：卷。 2’曲目列表如下：</strong> </p><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="29" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>朱莉娅·杰克林——《腰部以下死了》</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="29" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>考特尼·巴尼特 – “节礼日布鲁斯（演示）”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="29" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1